title: [Morgahan's Outfitting]
description: Beneath an oak beam ceiling, a mounted fish skeleton hangs on one of the dark oak walls.  A low wrought iron table sits in one corner while a stuffed grizzly bear rests on the oak floor.
Beneath an oak beam ceiling, a pair of wooden snowshoes hangs on one of the pale oak walls.  A low wrought iron table sits in one corner while an iron candelabra rests on the oak floor.
